comments: I noticed that all of the alien words began with the letter 'S' and also ended in 'YKS' or 'OKS'. That made it more challenging to associate the image with the correct word. Usually when memorizing words or images I use photonics to make it easier to remember. Since they all sound so similar, it made me have to focus more on the following three letters after the first S and ignore the beginning letter and ending 3 letters. It was hard at first because all of the words are very similar, but once I got in the groove and focused on the following three letters, it became a little easier.
